manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "caddyipscanner"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "caddyipscanner"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
trust-dns-resolver = "0.23.2"
walkdir = "2.5.0"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
lto = true
strip = true

[profile.release.package]
